until yesterday.

689
00:37:51,569 --> 00:37:53,037
You ogled her, didn't you?

690
00:37:53,104 --> 00:37:54,005
This is on you!

691
00:37:54,071 --> 00:37:56,407
How can you say that
when I have such innocent eyes?

692
00:37:56,474 --> 00:37:58,976
I hope she hasn't gone
to Kabukicho or somewhere.

693
00:37:59,043 --> 00:38:01,279
They say To-yoko is a rough place.

694
00:38:01,345 --> 00:38:03,014
Toyoko? You mean Norengai?

695
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:06,017
There's a spot
where runaway girls tend to gather.

696
00:38:06,083 --> 00:38:07,151
What are you doing here, Inoue?

697
00:38:07,852 --> 00:38:08,953
Junko.

698
00:38:09,020 --> 00:38:09,854
Huh?

699
00:38:10,388 --> 00:38:11,422
Junko--

700
00:38:21,799 --> 00:38:23,134
