745
00:40:17,548 --> 00:40:18,649
Stop it, Mr. Ogawa.

746
00:40:18,716 --> 00:40:22,086
If this were a drama,
it's like you only tuned in midway.

747
00:40:22,153 --> 00:40:25,556
If you enjoy it, wouldn't you want
to watch the entire series from the top?

748
00:40:26,924 --> 00:40:30,461
Actually, I've never watched
a series all the way through.

749
00:40:31,128 --> 00:40:34,131
