00:42:58,909 --> 00:43:00,210
They're gone.

784
00:43:01,612 --> 00:43:02,913
Everything okay?

785
00:43:05,716 --> 00:43:07,017
Let's see…

786
00:43:09,053 --> 00:43:12,923
The Skytree and Enoshima were both pretty,

787
00:43:13,891 --> 00:43:15,726
but my favorite place was…

788
00:43:25,903 --> 00:43:27,171
Junko!

789
00:43:30,608 --> 00:43:31,775
Jail…

790
00:43:33,277 --> 00:43:34,144
